      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "BZZZZZ or ZZZZzzzz Pt. 2",
        "Client": "Fussy Girlfriend",
        "Description": "Ugh! My soon to be ex-boyfriend\r\nhas done lost his mind! He thinks\r\nSomnacanth are longer than Khezu.\r\nHELLO! The stretchy necks!? Duh!\r\nI\u0027ve had it with him. I\u0027m SO done...\r\nAnyway, can you go out there and\r\ngive Khezzy my number? Thanks!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Khezu and a Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Querelle de couple, partie 2",
        "Client": "Petite-amie ind\u00E9cise",
        "Description": "Mon copain raconte n\u0027importe\r\nquoi. Il pense qu\u0027un Somnacanth\r\nest plus grand qu\u0027un Khezu. Et\r\npuis quoi encore ?! Il veut\r\npas en d\u00E9mordre, m\u00EAme si\r\n\u00E9videmment, c\u0027est moi\r\nqui ai raison. \u00C0 toi de trancher !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Khezu et un Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Colli lunghi o code alte?",
        "Client": "Fidanzata capricciosa",
        "Description": "Il mio ragazzo \u00E8 fuori di\r\ntesta. Dice che i Somnacanth\r\nsono pi\u00F9 alti dei Khezu. MA\r\nTI PARE?! \u00C8 ovvio che i Khezu\r\nsono pi\u00F9 alti, ma lui insiste.\r\nSe non vuole darmi retta,\r\ndovrai pensarci tu!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Khezu e un Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Langer Hals oder Schwanz?",
        "Client": "Pingelige Freundin",
        "Description": "Mein Freund hat sie nicht\r\nalle. Er glaubt, Somnacanth\r\nsind gr\u00F6\u00DFer als Khezu. HALLO?!\r\nKhezu sind eindeutig s\u00FC\u00DFer,\r\naber er gibt es nicht zu. Tja,\r\nich sch\u00E4tze, dann musst du den\r\nStreit f\u00FCr uns entscheiden!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Khezu und einen Somnacanth.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00BFRonquido o zumbido? 2.\u00AA parte",
        "Client": "Novia exigente",
        "Description": "\u00A1Ugh! El que va a ser mi exnovio\r\nest\u00E1 loco. \u00A1Dice que un Khezu es\r\nmenos largo que un Somnacanth!\r\n\u00BFHola? \u00A1\u00BFCon ese cuello largo?!\r\n\u00A1Bah! Estoy harta, que le den.\r\nOye, \u00BFme encuentras a un Khezito\r\npara darle mi n\u00FAmero? \u00A1Gracias!",
